						               													<description>This game is really simple to play, even for players who don&amp;rsquo;t love word games at all. It's super easy to compose a word related to the theme: you can use all the letters you want, not only the ones in your hand, and creativity and puns are welcome! No frustration in sight!&amp;#10;Of course, you must try to find a word that grants you a higher score than your opponents&amp;rsquo;!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;At the start of the game the Theme is revealed and you receive 8 Letter Cards:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;    1 - Choose the Letter you like and pass the others to the player at your left&amp;#10;    2 - Repeat point 1 until there are no more cards to pass. Receive from the right, pick one, pass to the left. Easy, right?&amp;#10;    3 - Compose a word related to the Theme, using as many of your Letters as you can!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The player who finds the word with the highest value wins the current round and scores 1 point. When a player scores the third point, the game ends and that player wins the game. If 2 or more player find a word with the same value, they all score 1 point. If 2 or more players reach the third point in the same round, they share the victory (this happens rarely).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
